Map Name: awp_lebanon_1994
Version: 1.0

Description: Isnt India kinda Boring? How bout Lebanon?
Its a pretty challenging Map... You can choose to go Onto the bridge and awp opposing bridgers.
Or stay low with cover and snipe your way through!
Extract the .RAR File to your cstrike folder within your steamapps. There is also a .NAV for BOTs!
Enjoy!

www.hellclan.co.uk
